OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fvery warm evening for many and staying
OL,7,Fsunny for most. Isolated thunderstorms
OL,8,Fare possible, potentially bringing
OL,9,Flarge hail and frequent lightning, but
OL,10,Fmost places staying entirely dry.
OL,11,FRemaining warm overnight with often
OL,12,Fclear skies.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day,
OL,15,Falthough there is a small chance of
OL,16,Fthe odd shower developing and perhaps
OL,17,Fa few thunderstorms later. Not as hot
OL,18,Fbut still feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
