OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying largely dry with some sunshine
OL,7,Fbut the odd shower is possible at
OL,8,Ftimes. Very warm initially but turning
OL,9,Fsomewhat cooler by the weekend.
OL,10,FCoastal mist and low cloud possible.
